data.description: Welcome to this beautiful Cap Cod Two-Story home in West Akron! You'll walk in the front door where you'll notice a spacious living room which leads to the beautiful kitchen, as well as new windows. This property has been remodeled and has three bedrooms, one full bath a half bath and a two car detached garage. The built-ins, intricate detailed flooring add to this property's character! The kitchen is sure to be enjoyed by those who have a love for cooking and for those who love to entertain. This well maintained three bedroom home is move-in ready. Beautiful home inside and out. Please schedule your private showing today
